                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:rowCount 3 ;
                                    oc:tableCaption "### Range Queries" ;
                                    oc:tableMarkdown """| Query | Description | Example |
|-------|-------------|---------|
| `n..n` | Between range | `stars:10..50` |
| `n..*` | Greater than or equal | `stars:10..*` (same as `>=10`) |
| `*..n` | Less than or equal | `stars:*..10` (same as `<=10`) |
""" ] ;
